ai-ja266:1.1_0: “What did you do with a jackal?
ai-ja266:1.2_0: and doesn’t try to get food.
ai-ja266:1.3_0: This is he who has come from a meal:
ai-ja266:1.4_0: Why don’t you shatter the breath?”
ai-ja266:2.3_0: For he who has abandoned a woman,
ai-ja266:2.4_0: Therefore I will move the palms.”
ai-ja266:3.1_0: by a family in which I’m born.
